<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Muhammad Danial Farooq | Portfolio</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e3a8a);
color:white;
}

.hero{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
min-height:100vh;
padding:40px;
}

.container{
max-width:1200px;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:space-between;
gap:60px;
flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.text{
flex:1;
}

.text h3{
font-size:25px;
color:#93c5fd;
}

.text h1{
font-size:60px;
margin:15px 0;
}

.text h1 span{
color:#38bdf8;
}

.text p{
font-size:18px;
color:#d1d5db;
line-height:1.8;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
padding:15px 35px;
margin-right:15px;
border-radius:40px;
background:#38bdf8;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:600;
transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
background:white;
color:#0f172a;
transform:translateY(-4px);
}

.image{
flex:1;
text-align:center;
}

.image img{
width:340px;
height:340px;
border-radius:50%;
object-fit:cover;
border:8px solid #38bdf8;
box-shadow:0 0 40px #38bdf8;
}

.about{
background:white;
color:#222;
padding:80px 10%;
}

.about h2{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.about p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.container{
flex-direction:column-reverse;
text-align:center;
}

.text h1{
font-size:42px;
}

.image img{
width:250px;
height:250px;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<section class="hero">

<div class="container">

<div class="text">

<h3>Hello, I'm</h3>

<h1><span>Muhammad Danial Farooq</span></h1>

<p>
BS Computer Science Student at IST Islamabad.<br>
Passionate Web Developer learning HTML, CSS, JavaScript and building modern websites and applications.
</p>

<a href="cv.pdf" class="btn">📄 Download CV</a>

<a href="mailto:muhammaddanialfarooq150@gmail.com" class="btn">💼 Hire Me</a>

</div>

<div class="image">

<img src="profile.jpg" alt="Muhammad Danial Farooq">

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="about">

<h2>About Me</h2>

<p>
I'm Muhammad Danial Farooq, a Computer Science student with a passion for web development and software engineering. I enjoy creating modern, responsive websites and am currently working on SportBook Pakistan, a sports booking platform. I'm always looking for opportunities to learn, collaborate, and build useful digital products.
</p>

</section>

</body>
</html>
